      "title": "Violin Concerto No. 5",
      "apple_classical_url": "https://classical.music.apple.com/us/work/niccolo-paganini-1782-pp154",
      "wikipedia_url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Violin_Concerto_No._5_(Paganini)",
      "wikipedia_extract": "The Violin Concerto No. 5 in A minor was composed by Niccolò Paganini in 1830. It is one of the most widely performed of Paganini's last violin concertos. A typical performance lasts about 40 minutes. It was Paganini's latest-composed concerto.",
